# ShellSpec configuration for harm-cli

## Output format
--format documentation
--color

## Shell to use (bash 5+ required)
--shell /opt/homebrew/bin/bash

## Coverage (uncomment to enable)
# --kcov

## Fail fast (uncomment to stop on first failure)
# --fail-fast

## Random execution order (uncomment for randomization)
# --random

## Warnings
# Warnings are informational only (stderr output expected in complex tests)

## Execution
--jobs 1
